review:
Thanks to Dr. Dilshad for extracting my wisdom tooth which caused a severe pain to me for months. She gave good medicine for the healing too. I had a wonderful time at the clinic too which made me feel comfortable without any hesitation.
Once again Thank you doctor for your treatment.

Prime dental clinic doctors helped in completing wisdom teeth removal and root canal treatment. Considering that I have crooked teeths, it was not at all easy but still managed to complete the treatment safely and with less pain. Doctors are thorough professionals and experience high quality treatment at affordable cost. All of them carries good attitude, humble at heart and treated patients like me with care and affection. They have most latest technologies available like digital x-ray so I dont have to go out or spend additional cost which is added advantage. Waiting time is less and atmosphere is friendly and welcoming. I would highly recommend them to my friends and family members.
